latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Have you ever tasted Italian Soppressata? It is a type of salami made with leaner cuts that is coarsely grounded. To enjoy Soppressata at its best, we paired it with Italian Salami, Provolone cheese, almonds, and olives in our AperiTime tray. Find it at your local retailer

latestPosts.caption:
♋️ LEO × SPECK ITALIANO
You’re bold, magnetic, and born to steal the spotlight — just like our Speck Italiano.
With its delicate saltiness, signature spices, and that unmistakable smoky aroma, this isn’t just any cold cut. It’s the star of the charcuterie board.
Let’s be real: when you show up, all eyes are on you. And when Speck’s on the table, it doesn’t just sit there — it performs.🔥

latestPosts.caption:
📌 June 30, 2025, Somewhere Nowhere: a memorable date and place where we celebrated our first 100 years of history in the heart of the Big Apple.
A century of passion, tradition, and flavor wrapped into one magical night — with music, creative boards featuring Italian-made charcuterie, an extraordinary skyline, and the energy of those who shared this important milestone with us. ✨

Here’s to the next 100 years — together 🥂

#Veroni #Veroni100 #Veroni100thAnniversary #charcuterie #charcuterieboard #italianquality

🔥 Bold flavor, Italian soul.
 Say hello to our Soppressata — a spicy salami with just the right kick, elevated by the aroma of fennel seeds.
 Crafted in Italy, sliced in the USA, and packed in our eco-friendly tray to keep every bite as fresh as the first.
 Authentic taste, modern touch. 🇮🇹♻️

#Veroni #charcuterie #charcuterieboard #italianquality #taste #authenticquality #soppressata

What a night to remember! ✨
On June 30th, we celebrated 100 years of Veroni on a breathtaking rooftop in New York City.
A heartfelt thank you to everyone who joined us and to all those who have stood by our side throughout this incredible journey. Your support means the world to us.
Here’s to the next century of flavor, tradition, and passion! 🥂
